<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>About Wikipedia Top 100</title>
    <link href='css/fonts.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <link href='css/chart.css' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <style>

    .top-area {
        background-color: #fbfbfb;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .top li {
        display: inline-block;
        list-style: none;
    }

    .top ul {
        margin: 0em;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
        font-size: 0.9em;
    }

    .top li {
        padding: 0.5em 2em 0.5em 0;
    }

    .others-area {
        display:none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 1em 0;
        color: #fbfbfb;
        background-color: #0098D8;
        text-align: center
    }

    .others {
        text-align: center;
    }

    .others {
        width: 58%;
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .about {
        width: 40%;
        display: inline-block;
    }

     @media (max-width: 660px) {
        .others, .about {
            width: 90%;
            padding: 0 1em;
        }
    }

    .container, .about {
        vertical-align: top;
    }

    .others ul {
        margin: 0;
        list-style: none;
    }

    .others li {
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 0.5em;
        border: 2px solid #222;
        width: 150px;
        border-radius: 7px 7px 7px 7px;
        -moz-border-radius: 7px 7px 7px 7px;
        -webkit-border-radius: 7px 7px 7px 7px;
    }

    .others li:hover {
         background-color: rgba(224, 233, 251, 1);
        -webkit-transition: background-color 500ms linear;
        -moz-transition: background-color 500ms linear;
        -o-transition: background-color 500ms linear;
        -ms-transition: background-color 500ms linear;
        transition: background-color 500ms linear;
    }


    .others a {
        display: block;
        padding: 1em;
        margin: 0;
        color: #0098D8;

    }

    body {
        background-color: #fbfbfb;
    }

    .feeds {
        margin: 0 2em;
    }

    .feeds-icon {
        margin: 0 0.5em;
    }

    </style>
    <!-- 
        Generated: {meta.generated}
    -->
</head>
<body>

    <div class="top-area">
        <div class="top container">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li>More languages</li>
                <li><a href="https://blog.hatnote.com/">Blog</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="others-area">
        <div class="others container">

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="header">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Wikipedia <span class="ultra">Top 100</span></h1>
            <p>The most-visited Wikipedia articles, updated daily.</p>
            <div class="subtitle light"><span class="issue_nav left"> </span><p class="center"></p><span class="right issue_nav"></span>
            <br style="clear: left;" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="others">
            <h2>More  Wikipedia languages</h2>
            <ul>
                {#languages}
                <li><a href="{url}">{name}</a></li>
                {/languages}
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="about">
            <h2>About</h2>
            {about|s}
            <h2>RSS Feeds<img src="img/feed.png" class="feeds-icon"></h2>
	    <p>Stay up to date on the most visited Wikipedia articles and more, via <a href="https://ifttt.com/recipes/351696-daily-wikipedia-top-100">IFTTT</a> or your <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comparison_of_feed_aggregators">favorite feed reader</a>.</p>
            <ul class="feeds">
                {#feeds}
                <li><a href="{url}" class="feed">{name}</a></li>
                {/feeds}
            </ul>
	    <p>Want to see a list of the most visited articles in another language of Wikipedia? So do we! Please <a href="https://github.com/hatnote/top/issues">send a request</a> and let us know if you can help translate the templates.</p>
        <h2>Data &amp; feeds</h2>
        <p>Per-day JSON data is available at <code>/en/wikipedia/2026/7/10.json</code> (same path as the HTML page with <code>.json</code> extension). RSS feeds are at <code>/feeds/{lang}{project}.rss</code>. Machine-readable site information is at <a href="/llms.txt">/llms.txt</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-9LD7M2WME2"></script>
    <script>window.dataLayer=window.dataLayer||[];function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}gtag('js',new Date());gtag('config','G-9LD7M2WME2');</script>
</body>
</html>
